query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'magento',
'mathoverflow',
'pt',
'unix')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('banco-de-dados',
'boot',
'centos',
'command-line',
'cv.complex-variables',
'forms',
'magento-2.1',
'mg.metric-geometry',
'networking',
'nodes',
'security',
'shell',
'software-installation')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Curious',
'Custodian',
'Necromancer',
'Notable Question',
'Scholar',
'Student',
'Supporter',
'Teacher') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
